AB  - This article reviews motivations for going beyond traditional business teaching material into the realm of films, memoirs, and novels. Included are suggestions of specific examples of films, memoirs, and novels which have a place in teaching the international business environment in less developed countries. An extensive annotated bibliography of films, memoirs, and novels is provided.
